Privacy Policy
-----------------

Effective date: 24 January 2026
Financial Planning Calculator respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how information is collected and used when you use our mobile application.

Information We Collect
----------------------------
We may automatically collect certain non-personal information when you use the app, including:
1. Device type and model
2. Operating system
3. App usage statistics
4. Crash reports
5. General location (country/region)

Analytics
-----------
We use third-party analytics services to understand how users interact with the app and to improve performance and user experience. These services may collect:
1. Device identifiers
2. Usage data
3. Performance and crash data

Advertising
--------------
This app displays ads using third-party advertising providers. Ad networks may collect:
1. Advertising ID
2. Device information
3. Approximate location
4. Ad interaction data
This information is used to show relevant advertisements and measure ad performance. You can disable personalized ads anytime from your deviceâ€™s ad settings.

Data Sharing
